{"body": "As for changing vendor code, I'm not sure what the standard practice is among rails developers, but I don't see some amount of changes can be avoided--sometimes bugs will show up in vendor code and it could be a bigger security issue to leave them as-is than to fix them.  If I'm the first to try to do this in rails (which seems unlikely), we need to discuss this in more detail--what sort of security issues are you concerned about?", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/9328997", "created_at": "2012-10-11T05:27:49Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/7901#issuecomment-9328997", "updated_at": "2012-10-11T05:27:49Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 7901, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/betesh/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/betesh/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/betesh/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/betesh", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/betesh/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/betesh", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/betesh/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/b8dc4b76792ff3c8cd993aa4c9c467f6?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F1c950f82143f74f12fe74420234ea39c.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/betesh/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/betesh/received_events", "gravatar_id": "b8dc4b76792ff3c8cd993aa4c9c467f6", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/betesh/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "betesh", "type": "User", "id": 2154282, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/betesh/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "5237f7cfbd3543c15100b12c"}, "id": 9328997, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/7901"}
